Just some refactoring notes...

# SoundBuffer

## addition or concatination

- [X] in-place add
- [X] add and copy
- [X] concatinate

## subtraction

- [X] in-place subtract
- [X] subtract and copy

## multiplication

- [X] in-place multiplication
- [X] mult and copy

## division

- [x] in-place division
- [x] divide and copy

## mix operator

- [x] in-place mix
- [x] mix into copy
- [x] right-aligned / left-aligned mixes

## built-in methods

- [x] clear -- fill with zeros
- [x] copy
- [x] dub
- [x] graph -- plot the waveform

## mixins

- [ ] cloud -- graincloud
- [ ] clip -- hard clip to minval/maxval
- [ ] softclip -- fx.softclip
- [ ] convolve -- fft.conv
- [ ] cut
- [ ] fcut -- frames
- [ ] rcut
- [ ] env
- [ ] fill -- truncate or loop to desired length
- [ ] blocks -- iterate over buffer in blocksize blocks
- [ ] grains -- iterate over buffer in variable-sized grains
- [ ] max -- absolute value max
- [ ] mix -- mix in place with sound or list of sounds
- [ ] pad -- pad with silence at start or end
- [ ] pan
- [ ] remix
- [ ] repeat
- [ ] reverse
- [ ] reversed
- [ ] speed
- [ ] vspeed
